test_even_range:
assert [6] == [14, 16, 18]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 14
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 16
  Full diff:
  - [14, 16, 18]
  + [6]
test_large_range:
assert [6, 7] == [7, 8, 9]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 7
  Right contains one more item: 9
  Full diff:
  - [7, 8, 9]
  + [6, 7]
